snippet.title: Yerba Mate Tycoon Trailer
snippet.description:
Buy on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1404560/Yerba_Mate_Tycoon/

Join us on Discord: (Yerba Mate + Yerba Mate Tycon Discord)
https://discordapp.com/invite/bDTu8HX

Follow me on Facebook:
https://www.facebook.com/donislawdev/

And Twitter:
https://twitter.com/donislawdev

You can also join my e-mail newsletter so that you won't miss the game release:
https://emailoctopus.com/lists/b0519df3-2425-11e9-a3c9-06b79b628af2/forms/subscribe

Casual Indie Management PC game, at least I'm honest at the trailer:-}


*This is alpha trailer, many things can change, Funny guy with mustache is not without mustache :-}
